data.description:
Nestled at the foothills of the majestic Sangre de Cristo Mountains lies Crestone, Colorado – a haven of tranquility and natural beauty. Embrace a life of serenity in this recently constructed residence set on xx acres of untouched wilderness. As you step inside, you're greeted by the warm embrace of maple floors, inviting you to explore further.

The heart of the home boasts an expansive open floor plan, flooded with natural light from its southern exposure, casting a golden glow that dances across the rooms. Here, every corner whispers tales of comfort and contentment, inviting you to unwind and embrace the quietude that surrounds you.

Escape to your private sanctuary within this abode's three spacious bedrooms and two baths, where relaxation is inevitable. But if space is what you desire, the oversized kitchen beckons you to indulge your culinary passions and create memories that will last a lifetime. Enjoy your bedroom fireplace and great room wood stove and whole house air conditioning in the summer!

Yearning for even more room to roam? Venture downstairs to the unfinished basement, a blank canvas awaiting your imagination to breathe life into it. Whether you envision a cozy retreat, a home theater, or a sprawling entertainment space, the possibilities are as boundless as the Colorado sky.

The magic doesn't end within the confines of this home – the owner's dedication to privacy extends beyond its walls. With additional land available for purchase, you can secure your own slice of paradise, ensuring uninterrupted moments of solitude and communion with nature.

Want more? Use it for an air BnB (VRBO) when you are away!

In Crestone, Colorado, this idyllic retreat isn't just a house – it's a sanctuary where dreams take flight, and the symphony of nature serenades your soul. Welcome Home.

Note: the extra lots are 3645C harmony Court (a double lot - $45,000 and 3646 Harmony Court $20,000 are available to you (not listed yet), for complete privacy.
